    "phase_1": "Kya aapke 87% bade faisle, aapka dimaag khud nahin leta?",
    "phase_2": "Nahin, main subconscious ki baat nahin kar raha. Main baat kar raha hoon ek chhipe 'dark mode' ki, jo aapke har kadam ko control karta hai, aur aapko khabar bhi nahin hoti.",
