    "phase_4": "Woh dabaav ek programming hai. Jab dimaag 3,291 baar 'decision fatigue' ka shikaar hota hai, tab yeh 'dark mode' control le leta hai. Aur uske 47% faisle, aapke nahin hote.",
    "phase_5": "Toh yaad rakhiye, aapka dimaag shayad khud hi apne 87% bade faisle nahin leta."
